# Ozerny, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Ozerny (; , Nuurta) is a rural locality (a settlement) in Yeravninsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 427 as of 2010. There are 7 streets.
Geography
Ozerny is located 57&nbsp;km north of Sosnovo-Ozerskoye (the district's administrative centre) by road. Khorga is the nearest rural locality.
